   <conbody>
      <p>To change enabled Probe components on a single instance of a Probe cluster, perform the following:</p>
      <codeblock>$ vi /opt/ericsson/eea/conf/probe_config.py
$ besr_local force-reload</codeblock>
      <p>Default is to execute the service operation on all enabled components. For example, perform the following to restart all components:</p>
      <codeblock>$ besr_local restart</codeblock>
      <p>If a component is specified, the service operation is executed only on the given component. For example, perform the following to restart the gtpc component:</p>
      <codeblock>$ besr_local restart gtpc</codeblock>
   </conbody>
</concept>